author: USA TODAY, Adrianna Rodriguez and Lorenzo Reyes, USA TODAY
title: Nurses read names of colleagues who died of COVID-19 in protest outside White House
description: National Nurses United organized the protest to call attention to the thousands of health care workers  who were infected by the coronavirus.
content:
National Nurses United protest in front of the White House calling attention to the health care workers lacking PPE.
USA TODAY
